            <h1>Makeing Friends</h1>
            <p>Making friends with digital technology means understanding how to use devices, apps, and the internet in positive and meaningful ways. It’s about building healthy habits, staying safe online, and using technology to connect with others, learn new things, and solve problems. By using digital tools responsibly, we can make our experiences more enjoyable and productive while also protecting our well-being.</p>
